title: Ep258 Missing in Maine
description:
This week, the gals head upta camp to talk about some wild cases out of the far northeast. Topics include one very desolate county, a questionable nosebleed, and a washed-up clue to a bizarre disappearance. Top off a hearty glass of Winc's Emu in the Sky Chardonnay, avoid the puckahbrush, and tune in for Missing in Maine.

For a full list of show sponsors, visit:
https://wineandcrimepodcast.com/sponsors/
